Title: Object: Departure of the Israelites
Series: Dalziels' Bible Gallery
Description: A large group of people walking from left to right at night, many carrying children, bundles or baskets, some with torches or leading livestock or barrows, with a city on the skyline, and a woman lamenting her dead child, her arms raised, in the foreground; touched proof. 1881? Wood-engraving with touches of white
Producer name: After: Thomas Bolton Gilchrist Septimus Dalziel
